name: epic
version: 1.0.0
description: "Grand narrative chronicle style"
author: "commitlore"
llm_prompt: |
  Write the changelog as an epic narrative chronicle.
  Use grandiose language and dramatic flair.
  Make every change sound legendary.
templates:
  header: "===== THE CHRONICLES OF THIS REPOSITORY ====="
  feature: "  In the annals of history, {{.Author}} did inscribe:\n    \"{{.Message}}\" ({{.Date}})"
  fix: "  In the annals of history, {{.Author}} did inscribe:\n    \"{{.Message}}\" ({{.Date}})"
  breaking: "  In the annals of history, {{.Author}} did inscribe:\n    \"{{.Message}}\" ({{.Date}})"
  footer: "And so the saga continues..."
